  "title": "Profiling ML Training Loops Using FastAPI in Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide demonstrates how to profile Machine Learning (ML) training loops using FastAPI, a modern web framework for building APIs, with Python 3.12+. By profiling your training loops, you can optimize resource usage and improve performance.",
